functionEntry.name: drawPlayerButton
functionEntry.documentation:
Draws nicely Player 1 or 2 buttons, considering if they are
highlithed or not.
dc Where to draw it

label Label that indicates which player it is

score Score to draw in the button

justify Text justification (e.g. left, right)

highlighted True if the button is highlighted

Constructor

functionEntry.name: onResponse
functionEntry.documentation:
Event that happens on response of the user.
When the user replies YES, then the App exits.
